WHAT IS REPO?
Repo is container is which is used to store the code and manage code in a systematic way

VERSION CONTROL?
Version control systems are type of software which are used to track and manage each and every change in code, done by an 
individual or a team

Repo use?
To store the code 
track and mange each and every change done in code by team
multiple team members can work on code without any issue
can create several copies using branching systems to work on different task
no need to keep multiple version for build (as it provides tag feature)




